## 1. One-Line Summary

* **The Hook:** Xiom Jekyll & Hyde V47.5 is the ultimate modern "Goldilocks" tensor, perfectly balancing lethal top-end spin with an incredibly forgiving, confidence-inspiring short game.
* **Archetype:** Versatile Offensive / Balanced Looper.

